msgid "Radio Player Page"
msgstr "Radio Player Page"

#. Description of the plugin
#: radio-player-page.php
msgid ""
"Lightweight dedicated radio player page for Icecast, Shoutcast and MP3 streams. "
"Continuous live streaming with enhanced listener retention."
msgstr ""
"Página ligera dedicada al reproductor de radio para Icecast, Shoutcast y "
"emisiones MP3. Emisión en directo continua con mayor retención de audiencia."

